data.text: Delta Co. for Sweets and Food industries is considered one of the biggest companies in middle east , established in 1913 with the aim to produce and sale of different sorts of products including hard candy , Chocolate, Nougat, and Oriental Sweets . Juice, Wafer and Tahini lines were established and started working later . Since 1913 , We started our success story in sweets industry in local markets. Delta prepared itself to appear in international markets so, We stared to spread in many countries later . Superior Technology and better quality were the most reasons of Delta's name to be heard along the country which led our products to get great place among peers in the market . Delta Company, After nearly 100 years of valuable experience with the professional and dedicated staff ; tries its best with interest, presence and passion to improve its products as well .
